[DQR.IFRS.0126.9595] The statement 1004005 - Statement - Statement of cash flows, direct method (Statement) includes an inconsistent calculation. The value of the concept ifrs-full:CashFlowsFromUsedInOperatingActivities of 601,500,000 should be equal to the sum of its child components defined in the calculation linkbase. The sum of these child components is 625,500,000. The values of the addends is determined by adding the values of the child concepts with a decimal value of -5. All values in the financial statements should use the same decimal value. The values reported in the financial statement in the current reporting period of 2020-01-01 to 2020-12-31 should be complete if the financial statement is to be mathematically accurate and complete. The components of ifrs-full:CashFlowsFromUsedInOperatingActivities that should add to 601,500,000 are comprised of the following:
+ AnpassungenFurDenRuckgangDerHandelsUndSonstigenForderungenUndVerbindlichkeiten -3,000,000 + AnpassungenFurDenZunehmendenRuckgangAndererNichtfinanziellerVermogenswerte -8,200,000 + AnpassungenFurDieAbschreibungDesNutzungsrechtsAsset 24,200,000 + AnpassungenFurEinenErhohtenRuckgangAndererFinanziellerVermogenswerte -2,600,000 + AnpassungenFurEinenZunehmendenRuckgangAndererNichtFinanziellerVerbindlichkeiten 21,900,000 + AnpassungenFurEinenZunehmendenRuckgangDerSonstigenFinanziellenVerbindlichkeiten 3,000,000 + AnpassungenZinsertrgeZugeordnetBetrieblicherTtigkeit -1,000,000 + AnpassungenZinsertrgeZugeordnetBetrieblicherTtigkeit -1,000,000 + ErhalteneLeasingzinsenKlassifiziertAlsBetriebliche 400,000 + GezahlteLeasingzinsenKlassifiziertAlsBetriebliche 4,600,000 + AdjustmentsForAmortisationExpense 3,800,000 + AdjustmentsForDecreaseIncreaseInInventories -73,900,000 + AdjustmentsForDecreaseIncreaseInTradeAccountReceivable -20,500,000 + AdjustmentsForDepreciationExpense 19,000,000 + AdjustmentsForFinanceCosts 13,000,000 + AdjustmentsForFinanceIncome 5,000,000 + AdjustmentsForGainLossOnDisposalsPropertyPlantAndEquipment 600,000 + AdjustmentsForIncomeTaxExpense 26,700,000 + AdjustmentsForIncreaseDecreaseInDeferredIncome 52,800,000 + AdjustmentsForIncreaseDecreaseInTradeAndOtherPayables 154,900,000 + AdjustmentsForProvisions 4,700,000 + AdjustmentsForSharebasedPayments 24,000,000 + AdjustmentsForUndistributedProfitsOfAssociates -13,100,000 + IncomeTaxesPaidRefundClassifiedAsOperatingActivities 15,000,000 + InterestPaidClassifiedAsOperatingActivities 5,400,000 + InterestReceivedClassifiedAsOperatingActivities 600,000 + OtherAdjustmentsForNoncashItems 100,000 + ProfitLoss 369,100,000
The addends are calculated based on the calculation linkbase defined for 1004005 - Statement - Statement of cash flows, direct method (Statement). If addends are missing then the calculation tree should be amended. The rule will not add dimension components as the financial statement does not include a table. If dimensions are used on the statement then add a table to ensure that the dimensions are defined correctly.
